### TITLE ###
EmptyDocument
### DOCUMENT ###
### STDOUT ###
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "textDocument/publishDiagnostics",
  "params": {
    "diagnostics": [],
    "uri": "file:///test.rad"
  }
}
